## Griv AI Platform Demo

This project is a demonstration of the Griv AI Platform, an AI-powered omni-channel 
operations automation platform. It showcases the complete feature set including:

- Dashboard with real-time analytics
- Workitem management (leads, tasks, grievances, follow-ups)
- Contact management with type-based categorization
- Workflow builder with visual automation
- AI chat integration with token tracking
- Team management with ACL permissions
- Multi-tenant organization support
- ShadCN design system implementation

Built with React, TypeScript, and deployed on Vercel.